::Koj::
Koj watch WarMachine thinking come on stupid alittle closer.Koj waits as 
WarMachine reaches for the pod waiting till he gets a firm grip on it. Koj 
slams on the detonator and watches as 5 pods explode with a fury enough to 
shake the base.

::Inu-Yasha::
Inu-Yasha Uncloaks "Anybody want to come out and play everyone Charge."
Inu takes a lock on WarMachine and Fires 5 lancers at him.

::The Holocubes project::
The Cubes Project a 8 heavy armed warriors running out of the woods Fireing 
on the far side of the base. That being opposite side Koj is on.
